config BR2_PACKAGE_SIGMASTAR_VENC_POC
	bool "sigmastar-venc-poc"
	default n
	help
	  Experimental Sigmastar MI VENC proof-of-concept tools.
	  Disabled by default; enable only for manual VENC experiments.

	  The package builds small standalone tools that load libmi_sys.so
	  and libmi_venc.so at runtime with dlopen(), then inject NV12 frames
	  into the VENC input port and dump an H.265 elementary stream.

	  The included MI ABI header is reverse engineered and must be treated
	  as experimental until verified against an official Sigmastar SDK.
